  "knowledge_nodes": [
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_e3d404d0198f7e25",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_334ff0accb5b410d"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "想象一个重球 H 和一个轻球 L 从同一高度落下。 先分别考虑它们各自的“自然下落速度”，再考虑把二者用细绳绑成 复合体 HL 后一起下落，会得到什么结果。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "thought_experiment_env",
          "module": "setting",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_aab9003445df2fec",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_ddafbd5bca7f6f12"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "一个理想化的无空气阻力环境， 只保留重力作用，不让介质阻力参与落体过程。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "vacuum_env",
          "module": "setting",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_df66e0694c5ca5ad",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_9700beed75f85007"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "重的物体比轻的物体下落得更快。 下落速度与重量成正比。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "heavier_falls_faster",
          "module": "aristotle",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_a9ca4fd9f5070274",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_bd45db77c1eb0d3f"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "在日常空气环境中，从同一高度落下时，石头通常比羽毛更早落地； 重物看起来往往比轻物下落得更快。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "everyday_observation",
          "module": "aristotle",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_4106b1710e46373e",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_c2ce6f83402d503f"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "env"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "law"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在 {env} 中暂时接受 {law}： 轻球天然比重球下落更慢。于是当轻球与重球绑在一起时， 轻球应当拖慢重球，复合体 HL 的下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "deduce_drag_effect",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_66d50713e601243e",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_a990b93dacd62d5c"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "prediction_a"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "prediction_b"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "比较 {prediction_a} 与 {prediction_b}。 这两条结论针对同一个绑球系统、同一时刻、同一环境， 却分别断言“更慢”和“更快”，因此不能同时为真。 这暴露出亚里士多德落体定律在该思想实验中的内在矛盾。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "expose_mutual_exclusion",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_d6c7bca7e8a06693",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_fdb785aa74b1f866"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "gradient"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "observation"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "由 {gradient} 可知，介质越稀薄，轻重物体的速度差异越小。 因而 {observation} 更应被解释为介质阻力造成的表象， 而不是重量本身决定自由落体速度的证据。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "explain_everyday_observation",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_422bad5b75dd2df5",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_535db8ea513c6aa0"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "confound"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "env"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "support"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "verdict"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "如果 {verdict}，并且 {confound}，再加上 {support}， 那么在 {env} 这一无空气阻力的极限条件下， 最合理的预测是：不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "synthesize_equal_fall_prediction",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_8ca9a2b93b0e9307",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_4c34b6bb7330df19"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "复合体 HL 因轻球拖拽，下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "tied_pair_slower_than_heavy",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_a95c07b51e050bfb",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_df8f16e5fe84d89e"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "复合体 HL 总重量大于单独的重球 H，下落速度应快于 H。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "tied_pair_faster_than_heavy",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "contradiction",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_b6bb05362b879e90",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_16859c596a11a9ae"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "between": [
          "tied_pair_slower_than_heavy",
          "tied_pair_faster_than_heavy"
        ]
      },
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "同一定律对同一绑球系统同时预测\"更慢\"和\"更快\"，自相矛盾。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "tied_balls_contradiction",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_148c1b8d98f495b5",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_e26cef85fa3ccc52"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "亚里士多德\"重者下落更快\"的定律因绑球矛盾而不能成立。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "aristotle_contradicted",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_292f81b065df5b91",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_c06bcd74188c18d6"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "在水、油、空气等不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落， 会发现介质越稠密，速度差异越明显；介质越稀薄，差异越不明显。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "medium_density_observation",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_1e3724075272f3b5",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_01f3cfde04ead72c"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "介质越稀薄，轻重物体的下落速度差异越小。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "medium_difference_shrinks",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_61197e996f3dd38a",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_31b2d0f205e9215d"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "日常观察到的速度差异来自空气阻力，而非重量本身。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "air_resistance_is_confound",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_3d20684fe585a228",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_f1c7935e0aaab417"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "伽利略的斜面实验把下落过程放慢到可测量尺度后显示： 不同重量的小球在相同斜面条件下呈现近似一致的加速趋势， 与“重量越大速度越大”的简单比例律并不相符。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "inclined_plane_observation",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_315917e2f79d7ef7",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_06a8f28c86c854d9"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "斜面实验支持\"重量不是决定落体速度的首要因素\"。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "inclined_plane_supports_equal_fall",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_cfb4e927e732fb7b",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_eccb04450c85782f"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "在真空中，不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "vacuum_prediction",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "question",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_716c8ef657abaf41",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_76bde2bf42e76287"
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "能否在足够接近真空的条件下直接比较重球与轻球的下落时间？ 如果日常差异确实来自空气阻力，那么真正决定性的实验应当在几乎无介质的环境中完成。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "follow_up_question",
          "module": "follow_up",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_25dddf57cc6aae0d",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_cef3f5aee93241c9"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "drag_prediction_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "deduce_drag_effect"
      },
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "在 想象一个重球 H 和一个轻球 L 从同一高度落下。 先分别考虑它们各自的“自然下落速度”，再考虑把二者用细绳绑成 复合体 HL 后一起下落，会得到什么结果。 中暂时接受 重的物体比轻的物体下落得更快。 下落速度与重量成正比。： 轻球天然比重球下落更慢。于是当轻球与重球绑在一起时， 轻球应当拖慢重球，复合体 HL 的下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "drag_prediction_chain__apply_deduce_drag_effect",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_8c42bbb2570499b9",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_12f64fbc2c0fa1cf"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "contradiction_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "expose_mutual_exclusion"
      },
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "比较 复合体 HL 因轻球拖拽，下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。 与 复合体 HL 总重量大于单独的重球 H，下落速度应快于 H。。 这两条结论针对同一个绑球系统、同一时刻、同一环境， 却分别断言“更慢”和“更快”，因此不能同时为真。 这暴露出亚里士多德落体定律在该思想实验中的内在矛盾。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "contradiction_chain__apply_expose_mutual_exclusion",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_645d38ebf9ed901b",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_d5fffa7016ba1576"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "confound_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "explain_everyday_observation"
      },
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "由 介质越稀薄，轻重物体的下落速度差异越小。 可知，介质越稀薄，轻重物体的速度差异越小。 因而 在日常空气环境中，从同一高度落下时，石头通常比羽毛更早落地； 重物看起来往往比轻物下落得更快。 更应被解释为介质阻力造成的表象， 而不是重量本身决定自由落体速度的证据。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "confound_chain__apply_explain_everyday_observation",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_1f43c2bad5e7676d",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_ef88e3fe389c273c"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "synthesis_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "synthesize_equal_fall_prediction"
      },
      "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "如果 亚里士多德\"重者下落更快\"的定律因绑球矛盾而不能成立。，并且 日常观察到的速度差异来自空气阻力，而非重量本身。，再加上 斜面实验支持\"重量不是决定落体速度的首要因素\"。， 那么在 一个理想化的无空气阻力环境， 只保留重力作用，不让介质阻力参与落体过程。 这一无空气阻力的极限条件下， 最合理的预测是：不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。\n",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "synthesis_chain__apply_synthesize_equal_fall_prediction",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
